    HMA LAYOUT ARCHITECTURE (stable — do not revert to global website.layout xpath replace)

    All visitors (including logged-in designers): HMA topbar + header + footer always.
    no_header/no_footer keeps Odoo default chrome off HMA routes (other site pages unchanged).

    Snippet drop zones (always in DOM, visible only in active Website Builder via CSS):
      - #oe_structure_hma_editor at top of #wrap (page body snippets)
      - #footer.oe_structure inside HMA footer (footer snippets, Odoo convention)

    Do NOT gate chrome on QWeb "editable" — that flag is True for every designer even when
    not editing, which wrongly showed Odoo's default header/footer before.

    Pages must use t-call="hma_website.hma_website_layout" (not website.layout alone).
  -->

